title: Introducing: Malena Zavala
body:
Now usually I’m not a fan of psych-tinge indie – yet there’s just something that really speaks to me about this debut track from Argentinian born artist **Malena Zavala**.

In truth it’s perhaps more Youth Lagoon than Unknown Mortal Orchestra, with it’s addictive yet delicate melodies, _Should I Try_ serves as a stunning introduction to a colossally exciting new musician. Check it out below.
